commit.message:
Add Collection class

This commit adds a new list wrapper called Collection which holds
a list of resources as well as metadata associated with the list.
This has several usages like cursor-based pagination implemented
with stateful HTTP headers.

Fix inconsistent get method (compared to other verbs); add get_formatted

This commit makes Connection.get return a Response object just like
all other HTTP verb methods on Connection. It also adds a
get_formatted method which preserves the old behavior.

Merge pull request #18 from gwincr11/cg-documentation

More Docs

More Docs
Added docs to the readme to outline some of the api and how to work with
the library. Largely based off the ActiveResource gem but updated for
the differences in the library that I am aware of.
